edbackModal_main_3613984\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 06, 2025</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jqu1665703109428.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqu1665703109428.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jqu1665703109428.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jqu1665703109428\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__p_d109361e1_d109362e1_d109363e1\">u_target<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code><code class=\"ph codeph\">_blank</code> |\n        <code class=\"ph codeph\">_parent</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">_self</code> |\n        <code class=\"ph codeph\">_top</code></p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__section_rjt_gsh_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d799082e66\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__ul_aqp_hsh_bxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__li_d42512e1_d42513e1_d42514e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_blank</code>—load in new window or tab </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__li_d42515e1_d42516e1_d42517e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_parent</code>—load in the parent frame </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__li_d42518e1_d42519e1_d42520e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_self</code>—load in the same window </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__li_d42521e1_d42522e1_d42523e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">_top</code>—load in the full body of the window </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__section_vbk_3sh_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d799082e99\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__p_d109370e1_d109371e1_d109372e1\">Specify a value for this property when defining a\n        hyperlink, either as a hyperlink HTML control (for text links), or as an image HTML control\n        (if you want the image to be a link).</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__p_d109373e1_d109374e1_d109375e1\">The value of this field is concatenated with the\n        values of <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Link Text</span> for Hyperlink widgets or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Image\n          Source</span> for Image widgets, and <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Link Value</span> to provide the\n        content of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;a href&gt;</code> tag in the HTML layout.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__p_d109376e1_d109377e1_d109378e1\">Uniface uses the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">=</span> ProcScript\n        statement to evaluate the contents of this field at run time. Therefore, you can use a field\n        substitution to specify the desired target window. For example, you can enter\n          <code class=\"ph codeph\">%%TARGETWIN.MYENT.MYMODEL%%%</code> to use the contents of the TARGETWIN\n        field.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__section_xbl_jsh_bxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d799082e132\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jqu1665703109428__ul_esv_msh_bxb\">\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xff1719469149188.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xff1719469149188.html\" title=\"This widget defines a hyperlink in a static server page. (To use an image as a hyperlink, use the Image USP widget.)\">Hyperlink</a> (USP)</li>\n<li class=\"li\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypk1719469595014.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypk1719469595014.html\" title=\"This widget displays an image that can represent a hyperlink, have alternative text, or make use of other features that are not available in the picture control.\">Image</a> (USP)</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dmf1665703108475.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Link Text (u_hyperldispl)</a><p>Widget property that defines the visible text of a hyperlink in a static server page.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twd1665703108686.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Link Value (u_url)</a><p>Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/npf1665703108397.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Image Source (u_src)</a><p>Widget property that defines the path and file name of the image to display. This property sets the src attribute of the &lt;img&gt; tag in the HTML layout of the static server page.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613984\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613984\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Target Window (u_target) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 06, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Widget property in a static server page that determines the window into which the linked page is loaded. u_target = _blank | _parent | _self | _top Arguments _blank —load in new window or tab _parent —load in the parent frame _self —load in the same window _top —load in the full body of the window Description Specify a value for this property when defining a hyperlink, either as a hyperlink HTML control (for text links), or as an image HTML control (if you want the image to be a link). The value of this field is concatenated with the values of Link Text for Hyperlink widgets or Image Source for Image widgets, and Link Value to provide the content of the <a href> tag in the HTML layout. Uniface uses the = ProcScript statement to evaluate the contents of this field at run time. Therefore, you can use a field substitution to specify the desired target window. For example, you can enter %%TARGETWIN.MYENT.MYMODEL%%% to use the contents of the TARGETWIN field. Applies To Hyperlink (USP) Image (USP) Related Links Link Text (u_hyperldispl) Widget property that defines the visible text of a hyperlink in a static server page. Link Value (u_url) Widget property that defines the target URL of a hyperlink or image in a static server page. Image Source (u_src) Widget property that defines the path and file name of the image to display. This property sets the src attribute of the <img> tag in the HTML layout of the static server page. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}